      <section eId="sec_491">
        <num>491</num>
        <heading>Returns to be secret</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_491__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Any officer or employee of the state who willfully violates the\nprovisions of subdivision one or two of this section shall be dismissed\nfrom office and be incapable of holding any public office in this state\nfor a period of five years thereafter.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_491__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Cross-reference: For criminal penalties, see article thirty-seven\nof this chapter.\n  * NB Repealed July 5, 2028\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
